      <byline class="print_byline">By Florence Fabricant</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Fabricant, Florence</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Christopher Norman Chocolates makes special apple-shaped truffles on a stick; photo (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>They look like tiny candy apples, but these apple-shaped truffles on a stick are not at all for the little ones at Halloween. They are adult treats, made by Christopher Norman Chocolates, with a chocolate and caramel filling infused with apple and coated with marbleized chocolate and chopped hazelnuts. The truffles, about the size of lady apples, are $6 each at Balducci's, $8 in the food hall at ABC Carpet &amp; Home, and $35 for four, plus shipping, from www.eluxury.com.</p>
      </block>
